<h1 >农谚</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="javascript:;" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=271868" target="_blank" class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" nslog-type="90000102"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num"></span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="authorityListPrompt">
<div class="main-content-zj">
本词条由<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/science" target="_blank" class="nslog:7175">“科普中国”科学百科词条编写与应用工作项目</a>
审核
。</div>
</div>
<div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">农谚流传相当久远，不少古书上已有记载。农谚讲的是农业生产。广义的农业生产包括农、林、牧、副、渔五业，农之中还包括农作物、果蔬、蚕桑等，这些内容在农谚中都有。再说，农业生产离不开土壤、肥料、水分、温度以至于季节、气象、气候条件，这些方面在农谚中占有大量内容。农业生产又是由人在进行的，因此农谚中还有很多内容离不开人与人的关系，经营管理的经验等。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
农谚
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
farmer&#39;s proverb
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">解&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;释</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
关于农业生产的谚语
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">拼&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;音</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
nóng yàn
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">来&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;处</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
农民长期生产实践里总结的经验
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">举&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;例</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
“九耘谷无毛，三削麦无糟”
</dd>
</dl></div>
